There's hardly any produce.

641
00:51:26,440 --> 00:51:28,795
Well, that's it, the crops failed.

642
00:51:30,240 --> 00:51:34,473
And it's Rowan.
Rowan and the crops failed!

643
00:51:35,680 --> 00:51:37,079
Sacrifice.

