00:53:45,600 --> 00:53:51,278
♪ The things I'll show to you

663
00:53:52,720 --> 00:54:00,116
♪ Would you have a wondrous sight?

664
00:54:01,400 --> 00:54:07,237
♪ Mm-hm, the midday sun

